Package solid5ive.cams.data.entities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BalanceTransaction
    Incompleted features, this is an entity used to keep track of top-up and refund activities to further manage cash shrinkage.
    Canteen
    Entity class for Canteen records.
    Menu
    Entity class for menu item records, cacheable during runtime.
    MenuReference
    Entity class that records information of a menu item that is to be used for sales reporting.
    Order
    Entity class for a record of transaction between stall owners and customers, consist of food order information as well for sales reporting purpose.
    Orderline
    The entity class that records an entry of food order information in an order.
    Stall
    The entity class for the record of a stall in canteen, cacheable at runtime.
    User
    The entity class that records basic information about an user in the system.
    UserAccount
    The entity class that records account balance of an user.
    UserContact
    The entity class that records user contact information such as phone number, e-mail address, and postal address.
    UserPermission
    User permission is not supposed to be managed by our system (It is managed by school/higher level department).
    UserRole
    User role is not supposed to be managed by our system (It is managed by school/higher level department).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ContactType
    Represents three type of contact will be stored in database.
    MenuTag
    Enumeration for various tag that stall owner can use to highlight their menu item.
